{"tid":2412903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要幫政府合理化安心出行惡性措施？","createTime":"2021-02-18T09:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T10:35:18.000Z","uid":108418,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c8af6aad76f1f009a597d5b73ab66f65a8a435ff","tid":2412903,"uid":108418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"富臨唔CHECK人安心出行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2412494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2412494</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔係好明白啲人諗咩。<br />\n如果你反對政府嘅做法，點解你會選擇做政府嘅代理人去捉人唔用安心出安心出行？<br />\n你引用599G去督藍店灰，其實係授予599G呢條違憲嘅惡法直即執行嘅權力。<br />\n權力係來自人嘅行動，只有集體拒絕使用安心出行，反對599G，拒絕做599G執達吏，先可以抗衡呢條惡法。<br />\n二零一九到依家，究竟香港人幾時先會真正覺醒？<br />\n<br />\n利申，非熱狗，新東補選投天琦，仲好記得陳雲講過新香港成立後要處死梁天琦。我只係睇唔過眼想發洩下。"},{"pid":"c235f9d569d9d4242914f72c4e4cf1cb349f5d64","tid":2412903,"uid":46400,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"富臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />緊係要捉啦 支法犯法"},{"pid":"802094bb54f9c8194ddef7fb64161b8031a1f07e","tid":2412903,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"好明顯班廢柴借d意去食藍店姐，驚俾人周到咪諗d低能藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194aa470779bb12eb5f26e9d8124d00c557abce3","tid":2412903,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"又要黃店唔撚check<br />\n富臨唔check又搞鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要整條黃店唔撚check既篤灰list出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7774063100aceed02ff6cb193cffb72301edffdb","tid":2412903,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"樓主有道理<br />\n推<br />\n佢整惡法<br />\n就算係敵人我都唔會用黎捉佢<br />\n因為捉完佢，就會用黎捉我"},{"pid":"1a26a193b6b45830f446563c631297f243718b3e","tid":241